CatDescriptText: David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Men in military uniforms, including Army and Navy, and Pittsburgh Mayor David L. Lawrence wearing eye mask, singing in the Office of Mayor at City County Building
